John Sebastian Verney1

M, #320407, b. 30 August 1945

Last Edited=8 May 2011

John Sebastian Verney was born on 30 August 1945.1 He is the son of Sir John Verney, 2nd Bt. and Jeanie Lucinda Musgrave.2

John Sebastian Verney usually went by his middle name of Sebastian.1 He was educated at Eton College, Windsor, Berkshire, England .1 He succeeded as the 3rd Baronet Verney, of Eaton Square, City of Westminster [U.K., 1946] on 2 February 1993, but does not use the title.2 He lived in 2003 at 34 Gladstone Street, London, England .1

Ann Sybella Martha Farquhar1

F, #320408, d. 16 February 1907

Last Edited=3 Apr 2011

Ann Sybella Martha Farquhar was the daughter of Sir Thomas Harvie Farquhar, 2nd Bt. and Sybella Martha Rockcliffe.1 She married George Clive, son of Edward Bolton Clive and Hon. Harriet Archer, on 2 May 1835.1 She died on 16 February 1907.1

From 2 May 1835, her married name became Clive.1
